This template ("Template") is created by Xen-Shuto ("Author") for creating
Stellaris portrait mods. By downloading or using the Template, you agree to
the following terms.

1. COPYRIGHT
Copyright (c) 2025 Xen-Shuto. All rights to the Template belong to the Author.

2. PERMISSIONS
You may download and modify the Template for local use. You may publish your
own Stellaris portrait mods ("Work") based on this Template for non-commercial
purposes. A "Work" is defined as a mod that possesses its own originality and
is not a redistribution of the Template itself.

3. RESTRICTIONS
The following actions are strictly prohibited:
- Redistributing or publishing the Template (or modified versions of it)
  as a "template" or "resource pack."
- Impersonating the Author or publishing any content in a way that misleads
  others to believe it is the original Template or an authorized update
  provided by the Author.
- Presenting this Template or derivative Works as official content from 
  Paradox Interactive or any other third party.

4. COMMERCIAL USE
Commercial use of the Template or any Work derived from it is prohibited.

5. CREDITS (OPTIONAL)
When publishing your Work, it would be appreciated if you include:
- Credit to the Author: Xen‑Shuto
- A link to the original Template: https://github.com/Xen-Shuto/species_portrait_template

6. DISCLAIMER AND LIABILITY
THE TEMPLATE IS PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND. THE AUTHOR
SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES ARISING FROM THE USE OF THE TEMPLATE.
This Template is unofficial fan content and is not endorsed by or affiliated
with Paradox Interactive.

7. GOVERNING LAW AND UPDATES
This license is governed by the laws of Japan. The Author reserves the right
to update these terms at any time.

